rg/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Appearing at a red carpet event at theTrocadero, Williams, 51, wore aLouis Vuittonjumper paired with black shorts and a beige cap.\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1173, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile Yes, And?\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"singer Grande, 31, opted to wear a light pink dress adorned with a bow and white gloves.\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1283, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Standing alongside her was her Wicked co-starCynthia Erivowho plays Elphaba in the forthcoming musical movie in which Grande stars as Glinda.\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1426, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1353, \"end\": 1360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elphaba\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elphaba\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elphaba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elphaba\"}, {\"begin\": 1419, \"end\": 1425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glinda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Glinda\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glinda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glinda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheLondon-born actress, 37, wore an emerald green strapless dress with a hat, gold jewellery and matching green nails.\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1546, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Photos from rehearsals show Paparazzi singer Lady Gaga performing in black gloves with round pink props.\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1593, \"end\": 1602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is reportedly set to perform a version of Edith Piaf's La Vie en Rose alongsideCeline Dionas part of a glittering conclusion to the first ever opening ceremony being staged outside a stadium.\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1700, \"end\": 1710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\", \"score\": 0.9999999912251951, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Edith Piaf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Among the other stars pictured in front of theEiffel Towerwas The Vampire Diaries actressNina Dobrev.\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1913, \"end\": 1932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Vampire_Diaries\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1005461623547368e-33, \"text\": \"The Vampire Diaries\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Vampire_Diaries\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Vampire_Diaries\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 35-year-old opted to wear a black and red leather jacket, black handbag and white shorts.\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 2047, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Braving the rain on Friday afternoon was editor in chief ofAmericanVogueAnna Wintourand film directorBaz Luhrmann.\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2163, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While Wintour wore a blue vertically striped dressed with ballon sleeves, the Elvis director sported a cream coloured ensemble with a cap.\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2303, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MusicianJohn Legendalso appeared at the event, alongside his wife and TV presenterChrissy Teigen.\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2402, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Legend, who sang a version of John Lennon's Imagine in a\\u00a0 video during the 2021 opening ceremony inTokyo, wore a suit and white shirt while Teigen opted for a khaki-coloured ensemble with gold buttons.\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2605, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2434, \"end\": 2445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Lennon\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.282278226750794e-13, \"text\": \"John Lennon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Lennon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Lennon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 3467, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2649, \"end\": 2658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9999999997212399, \"rank\": 2.269213053280364e-10, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 2749, \"end\": 2758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9999999997212399, \"rank\": 2.269213053280364e-10, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http:/